reviewText: I actually likeed the concept of this movie,  but the execution was awful.  It was slow and instead terrorizing his victims, he pretty much bored them to death.
This movie is slow,predictable and not the least bit scary. Don't waste your time or your money. I couldn't even finish the last 15 mins. Too boring.
Highly recommend this movie! Great performances, I had fun but still got plenty scared. Great to watch with a group.
